rance (Ben Roddy)\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Act (Valentina Bor and Matt Edmonds)\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Dame (Brad Fitt)\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Dick Whittington, Shrewsbury\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Scene (Rocking Galley)\n|Won\n|-\n|Best Script\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Pantomime Newcomer (Lisa Davina Phillip)\n|Cinderella, Croydon\n|Nominated\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" |2014/15\n|Pantomime of the Year\n| rowspan=\"4\" |Sleeping Beauty, Crawley\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Script\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Female Baddie (Hilary O'Neil)\n|Won\n|-\n|Best Entrance ([[Stephen Mulhern]])\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Pantomime of the Year\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Dick Whittington, Sheffield\n|Nominated\n|-\n|Best Script\n|Won\n|-\n|Best Male Baddie (John Barr)\n|Won\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Production ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n|-\n|2018\n|''Mr Sunshine''\n|Producer & Director\n|Short\n|-\n|2017\n|''The Last Laugh''\n|Writer, Director & Producer\n|Short\n|-\n|2016\n|''Help! My Teachers are Aliens!''\n|Writer, Director & Producer\n|Short\n|-\n|2014\n|''Ski Fall''\n|Writer, Director & Producer\n|Short\n|-\n|2014\n|''Home Alone (in Eastry)''\n|Writer, Director & Producer\n|Short\n|}\n\n=== Self ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n|-\n|2018\n|''When Award Shows Go Horribly Wrong''\n|Himself\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|''Ant & Dec's Saturday Night Takeaway''\n|Himself\n|\n|-\n|1998\u20132001\n|''Don't Try This at Home!''\n|Presenter\n|5 Series\n|-\n|1999\n|''Night Fever''\n|Himself\n|3 Episodes\n|-\n|1999\n|''This Morning''\n|Himself\n|\n|-\n|1996\u20131998\n|''Dear Mr Barker''\n|Presenter\n|3 Series\n|-\n|1995\n|''Travel Bug''\n|Host\n|\n|-\n|1994\n|''Celebrity Squares''\n|Himself\n|\n|-\n|1989\n|''The Disney Club''\n|Presenter\n|\n|}\n\n=== Actor ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n|-\n|2000\n|''Talking TV''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1995\n|''For Amusement Only''\n|On Screen Participant\n|13 Episodes\n|-\n|1992\n|''Parallel 9''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1987\n|''Ou